column2: SELECT TOP # p.ra,p.dec,p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj,ISNULL(s.plate,#) as plate,ISNULL(s.mjd,#) as mjd,ISNULL(s.fiberid,#) as fiberid, &&& as filter FROM  #x x, #upload u,  BESTDR1..PhotoObj as p LEFT OUTER JOIN BESTDR1..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE  ( p.type = # OR p.type = #) AND u.up_id = x.up_id AND x.objID=p.objID ORDER BY x.up_id
